    text: 'A travel company has a Common Data Service (CDS) environment.\n\nThe company requires custom entities that track which regions clients have traveled to and the dates they traveled to these regions.\n\nYou need to create the entities and relationships to meet the requirements.\n\nWhich three actions should you perform? Each correct answer presents part of the solution.',
