    text: 'You are creating a Power Platform solution for a fitness studio. Members use the solution to track progress toward fitness goals. Personal trainers create programs with different exercises. Members can opt into a program to submit information about their progress with trainer-suggested exercises.\n\nFitness programs and exercises have specific durations, prices, and dates.\n\nYou need to ensure that members can see all of the exercises that a trainer suggests in their calendars.\n\nAvailable options:\nA. Standard table with Organization ownership\nB. Standard table with User or Team ownership\nC. Activity table with User or Team ownership\n\nMatch each data type to the correct option.',
