    text: 'Fabrikam, Inc. has two divisions. Fabrikam Residences rents units short-term to clients. Fabrikam Property Management maintains the units and manages contractors.\n\nClients and contractors are both stored in the Contact entity.\n\nThe manager of the Property Management business unit is a member of the Fabrikam Residences business unit, which has the root security role shown in the source material.\n\nThe manager cannot see the contact record shown in the Contact exhibit.\n\nYou need to ensure that the manager can view contact records owned by someone in the Residences business unit.\n\nFor each statement, select Yes if it achieves the goal. Otherwise, select No.\n\nSTATEMENTS:\n1. Modify the security inheritance.\n2. Move the manager to the root Fabrikam business unit.\n3. Expand the Read permission of the security role to be Business Unit level.',
