    text: 'A company uses Dynamics 365 Sales.\n\nYou need to configure the customer lookup search for email activity in the canvas app.\n\nHow should you complete the expression?\n\nFUNCTION OPTIONS SEEN IN ANSWER AREA:\n- IsBlank\n- IsType\n- AsType',
