    text: 'You need to configure the fields with the appropriate type.\n\nSelect the appropriate type for each field.\n\nFields:\n1. Doctor\'s name field on customer record\n2. Auto-populate Refill date field\n3. Doctor\'s name field in Doctor\'s entity\n\nAvailable types for field 1:\n- Lookup\n- Calculated\n- Text\n- Option set\n\nAvailable types for field 2:\n- Rollup\n- Calculated\n- Currency\n- Whole Number\n\nAvailable types for field 3:\n- Text\n- Lookup\n- Image\n- Option set',
