    text: 'You need to identify why employees are not receiving notification that nine customers are checked in and waiting in the repair area.\n\nAvailable components:\n- action\n- condition\n- expression\n- data operation\n\nSteps:\n1. outbound text\n2. nine customers in the store\n3. number of customers in the store',
